    </p>
    <p class="center-block">Install Lazo globally</p>
    <div class="code-wrapper center-block">
        <pre class="language-bash"><code class=" language-bash">npm install -g lazo --production</code></pre>
    </div>
    <p class="center-block">
        Clone Lazo <a href="https://github.com/lazojs/todomvc">TodoMVC</a>
    </p>
    <div class="code-wrapper center-block">
        <pre class="language-bash"><code class=" language-bash">git clone git@github.com:lazojs/todomvc.git</code></pre>
    </div>
    <p class="center-block">
        Start Lazo <a href="https://github.com/lazojs/todomvc">TodoMVC</a>
    </p>
    <div class="code-wrapper center-block">
        <pre class="language-bash"><code class=" language-bash">lazo start lazojs-todomvc</code></pre>
    </div>
    <p class="center-block">
        Open browser to <a href="http://localhost:8080">http://localhost:8080</a>
    </p>
